'''雷酸'''，是一种[[化合物|化合物]]，[[分子式|分子式]]为HCNO。它的[[雷酸银|银盐]]在1800年由[[爱德华·查尔斯·霍华德|爱德华·查尔斯·霍华德]]（Edward Charles Howard）发现，后来在1824年由[[尤斯图斯·冯·李比希|尤斯图斯·冯·李比希]]进行了研究。它是一种有机酸，是[[异氰酸|异氰酸]]的[[异构体|异构体]]，[[异氰酸|异氰酸]]银盐在一年后被[[弗里德里希·维勒|弗里德里希·维勒]]发现。<ref>{{cite journal
| title = Fulminic Acid in the History of Organic Chemistry
| author = F. Kurzer
| journal = [[J._Chem._Educ.|J. Chem. Educ.]]
| year = 2000
| volume = 77
| issue = 7
| pages = 851–857
| url = http://jchemed.chem.wisc.edu/journal/Issues/2000/Jul/abs851.html
| doi = 10.1021/ed077p851
| access-date = 2013-01-25
| archive-date = 2009-02-18
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090218004148/http://jchemed.chem.wisc.edu/journal/Issues/2000/Jul/abs851.html
| dead-url = no
}}</ref><ref>
{{cite journal
| title =  The Life and Work of Edward Charles Howard
| url =  https://archive.org/details/sim_annals-of-science_1999-04_56_2/page/113
| author = F. Kurzer
| journal =  [[Annals_of_Science|Annals of Science]]
| year =  1999
| volume = 56
| issue = 2
| pages = 113–141
| doi = 10.1080/000337999296445
}}</ref>1966年首次制得了雷酸。<ref>Beck, W. and Feldl, K. (1966), ''The Structure of Fulminic Acid, HCNO''. Angew. Chem. Int. Ed. Engl., 5: 722–723. {{doi|10.1002/anie.196607221}}</ref>

雷酸及[[雷酸盐|雷酸盐]]（如[[雷酸汞|雷酸汞]]）都非常危险，经常被用来作为[[雷管|雷管]]引爆其他[[炸药|炸药]]，是典型的[[起爆药|起爆药]]。蒸气也是有毒的。

